ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_SURVEYING_TITLE:0 "Surveying a Solar System"
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_SURVEYING_TITLE:0 "调查恒星系"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_SURVEYING_DESC:1 "§SSurveying§! other solar systems is how you effectively explore the galaxy. While §SSurveying§! other systems you may discover other £planet£ §SPlanets§! and potential §SResources§!. \n\nTo survey a system, go to the §SGalaxy Map§! (£m£), select a £science_ship£ §SScience Ship§! and right click on a nearby system and choose "Survey System"."
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_SURVEYING_DESC:1 "§S调查§!其他恒星系即可有效地探索星海。在§S调查§!其他恒星系时，你可能会发现其他 £planet£ §S行星§!或是潜在§S资源§!。\n\n要调查恒星系，前往§S星系地图§!（£m£），选择一艘 £science_ship£ §S科研船§!，然后右键点击邻近的恒星系并选择“调查恒星系”。"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_SURVEYING_INSTRUCTIONS:0 "§Y1.§! Select a Science Ship.\n§Y2.§! Assign a Scientist to the ship if needed.\n§Y3.§! Right-click on the arrow pointing to the systems nearby.\n§Y4.§! Select "Survey System""
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_SURVEYING_INSTRUCTIONS:0 "§Y1.§! 选择一艘科研船。\n§Y2.§! 如果没有船上没有科学家，指派一名科学家。\n§Y3.§! 右键点击指向邻近恒星系的箭头。\n§Y4.§! 选择“调查恒星系”"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_SURVEYING_ACTION:0 "Go to a Science Ship"
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_SURVEYING_ACTION:0 "前往科研船"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_ANOMALIES_TITLE:0 "Studying Anomalies"
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_ANOMALIES_TITLE:0 "研究异常现象"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_ANOMALIES_DESC:0 "§SAnomalies§! are curiosities that you may discover when §SSurveying§! other systems. Researching them generally (but not always) results in beneficial events for your §SEmpire§!. \n\nThe time it takes to §SResearch§! an anomaly depends on its difficulty rating and the skill of the assigned §SScientist§!. You can use the §SSituation Log§! (£f2£) in the left side menu to return to the §SAnomalies§! you have left unresearched."
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_ANOMALIES_DESC:0 "§S异常现象§!是你在§S调查§!其他恒星系时可能发现的奇异现象。研究异常现象基本（但不是全都）会为你的§S帝国§!带来有益事件。\n\n§S研究§!异常现象所需的时间取决于其难度等级和指派的§S科学家§!的技能。你可以使用左侧菜单中的§S情报日志§!（£f2£）来找到尚未调查的§S异常现象§!。"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_ANOMALIES_INSTRUCTIONS:0 "§Y1.§! Survey Systems around you to find Anomalies.\n§Y2.§! Open Situation Log in the left navigation panel.\n§Y3.§! Choose an available Anomaly and assign a Scientist to study it."
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_ANOMALIES_INSTRUCTIONS:0 "§Y1.§! 调查周围的恒星系，找到异常现象。\n§Y2.§! 打开左侧导航面板中的情报日志。\n§Y3.§! 选择一个可用的异常现象，指派一名科学家对其进行研究。"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_ANOMALIES_ACTION:0 "Open Situation Log"
