ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_TECHNOLOGY_TITLE:0 "Researching Technologies"
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_TECHNOLOGY_TITLE:0 "研究科技"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_TECHNOLOGY_DESC:0 "Technologies are divided into one of 3 areas: \n£physics£ §SPhysics§!, £society£ §SSociety§!, and £engineering£ §SEngineering§!. \n\nYou may research a technology in each area simultaneously. \nYour §SResearch§! speed is based on the amount of §SResearch§! your Empire generates, which is produced by £building£ §SBuildings§! and £district£ §SDistricts§! on colonized £planet£ §SPlanets§!, and by §SResearch Stations§! in owned star systems."
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_TECHNOLOGY_DESC:0 "科技划分为三个领域：\n£physics£§S物理学§!、£society£§S社会学§!和£engineering£§S工程学§!。\n\n你可以同时在每个领域中研究一项科技。\n你的§S研究§!速度取决于你的帝国产出的§S科研点数§!，它由已殖民£planet£§S行星§!上的£building£§S建筑§!、£district£§S区划§!和我们所属恒星系中的§S研究站§!来产生。"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_TECHNOLOGY_INSTRUCTIONS:0 "§Y1.§! Open Research from the left navigation panel.\n§Y2.§! Click on any empty slot and select one technology from the list to start researching it."
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_TECHNOLOGY_INSTRUCTIONS:0 "§Y1.§! 在左侧导航面板中打开科研。\n§Y2.§! 点击任何一个空白槽位，并从列表中选择一项科技开始研究。"
