ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_SPACE_STATION_TITLE:0 "Expanding using Starbases"
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_SPACE_STATION_TITLE:0 "利用恒星基地扩张"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_SPACE_STATION_DESC:0 "The most effective way of expanding the borders of your Empire is through the construction of §SStarbases§! (Outposts). This can only be done in systems that have already been §SSurveyed§!. \n\nTo build a Starbase, order a £construction_ship£ §SConstruction Ship§! to construct a §SStarbase§!. The presence of a §SStarbase§! allows for further construction of §SResearch Stations§! and §SMining Stations§!, as well as the colonization of any habitable £planet£ §SPlanets§! in the system."
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_SPACE_STATION_DESC:0 "扩张帝国边境最有效的手段是建设§S恒星基地§!（哨站）。这项工作只能在已经被§S调查§!过的恒星系中进行。\n\n建立§S恒星基地§!需要命令一艘£construction_ship£§S工程船§!来执行相应操作。§S恒星基地§!建好之后，您就可以在这个星系内建设§S研究站§!和§S开采站§!，当然还可以殖民其中的宜居£planet£§S行星§!。"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_SPACE_STATION_INSTRUCTIONS:1 "§Y1.§! Open the Galaxy View by clicking the button in the central bottom part of the screen.\n§Y2.§! Right-click an unclaimed system and select "Build an outpost""
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_SPACE_STATION_INSTRUCTIONS:1 "§Y1.§! 点击屏幕下方中央的按钮打开星系视图。\n§Y2.§! 右键单击任何一个无归属的恒星系，点选“建设一座哨站”"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_SPACE_STATION_ACTION:0 "Go to a Construction Ship"
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_SPACE_STATION_ACTION:0 "前往一艘工程船"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_COLONIZATION_TITLE:0 "Colonizing Planets"
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_COLONIZATION_TITLE:0 "殖民行星"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_COLONIZATION_DESC:0 "Colonizing other planets allows your £pops£ §SPopulation§! to spread beyond its initial planet and gains you access to more §SResources§! for your §SEmpire§!. Some £planet£ §SPlanets§! are generally more habitable than others, so consider where you settle new £colony_ship£ §SColonies§!. \n\nTo colonize a habitable planet, it must reside within the borders of your Empire, and have been surveyed by a £science_ship£ §SScience ship§!."
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_COLONIZATION_DESC:0 "殖民其他行星可以让你的£pops£§S人口§!流动至新的行星，为你的§S帝国§!获取更多§S资源§!。有部分£planet£§S行星§!会比一般的更宜居一些，因此好好考虑在何处设立你的新£colony_ship£§S殖民地§!。\n\n殖民一颗宜居行星需要它坐落于你的帝国边境之内，并且被£science_ship£§S科研船§!调查过。"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_COLONIZATION_INSTRUCTIONS:1 "§Y1.§! Select your shipyard in the Outliner (right side of the screen).\n§Y2.§! Select the Shipyard tab in the bottom of the Shipyard window.\n§Y3.§! Build a Colony ship.\n§Y4.§! Select a habitable planet and click "Colonize"."
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_COLONIZATION_INSTRUCTIONS:1 "§Y1.§! 在总览（屏幕右侧）中选择您的船坞。\n§Y2.§! 在船坞窗口的下方选择船坞选项卡。\n§Y3.§! 建造一艘殖民船。\n§Y4.§! 选择一颗宜居行星并点击“殖民”。"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_COLONIZATION_ACTION:0 "Go to a Habitable Planet"
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_COLONIZATION_ACTION:0 "前往一颗宜居行星"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_EXCAVATION_TITLE:0 "Excavating Archaeology Sites"
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_EXCAVATION_TITLE:0 "发掘考古遗址"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_EXCAVATION_DESC:0 "£archaeology£ §SArchaeological Sites§! can be discovered while §SSurveying§! or be uncovered after a £planet£ §SPlanet§! has been colonized. \n\nAs long as an §SArchaeological Site§! is within the borders of an §SEmpire§!, that §SEmpire§! can task a £science_ship£ §SScience Ship§! to excavate the site. The duration of an excavation is determined by the difficulty rating of the §SArchaeological Site§!."
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_EXCAVATION_DESC:0 "£archaeology£§S考古遗址§!可以在§S调查§!的过程中，或是在一颗£planet£§S行星§!的殖民过程中被发现。\n\n当一个§S考古遗址§!处于一个§S帝国§!的境内时，该§S帝国§!可以派遣一艘£science_ship£§S科研船§!前往发掘。发掘的时长由§S考古遗址§!的难度决定。"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_EXCAVATION_INSTRUCTIONS:1 "§Y1.§! Open the Situation Log in the left navigation panel.\n§Y2.§! Choose an Archaeological Site.\n§Y3.§! Start the Project."
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_EXCAVATION_INSTRUCTIONS:1 "§Y1.§! 在左侧导航面板打开情报日志。\n§Y2.§! 选择一座考古遗址。\n§Y3.§! 开始项目。"
