ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_BASIC_RESOURCES_TITLE:0 "Basic Resources"
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_BASIC_RESOURCES_TITLE:0 "基础资源"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_BASIC_RESOURCES_DESC:0 "Basic Resources involve £energy£ §SEnergy Credits§!, £minerals£ §SMinerals§! and £food£ §SFood§!. \n\nThese resources are produced primarily by the £building£ §SBuildings§! on your £planet£ §SPlanets§! or by §SMining Stations§!. The basic resources are all gathered and stockpiled on a monthly basis and ought to be quickly scouted, exploited, and developed."
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_BASIC_RESOURCES_DESC:0 "基础资源包含£energy£§S能量币§!、£minerals£§S矿物§!以及£food£§S食物§!。\n\n这些资源主要由您£planet£§S行星§!上的£building£§S建筑§!或者§S开采站§!产出。这些基础资源均以月为单位结算收获量和存储量，而且应当尽快搜寻和开发利用。"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_BASIC_RESOURCES_INSTRUCTIONS:1 "§Y1.§! Select the Construction Ship in the Outliner (right side of the screen).\n§Y2.§! Open the Galaxy View (bottom part of the screen).\n§Y3.§! Choose a claimed system, and right-click it.\n§Y4.§! Select Build Mining Stations"
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_BASIC_RESOURCES_INSTRUCTIONS:1 "§Y1.§! 在屏幕右侧的总览中选择工程船。\n§Y2.§! 打开星系视图（屏幕下方中央）。\n§Y3.§! 选择一个已拥有的星系，右键单击。\n§Y4.§! 点选建造开采站"
