ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_ABSTRACT_RESOURCES_TITLE:0 "Abstract Resources"
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_ABSTRACT_RESOURCES_TITLE:0 "概念资源"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_ABSTRACT_RESOURCES_DESC:0 "Abstract Resources represent the non-physical assets of £influence£ §SInfluence§! and £unity£ §SUnity§!. \n\n£influence£ §SInfluence§! is earned by having other Empires as §SRivals§! or §SProtectorates§!. Influence is often spent on expanding your borders through §SStarbases§! and §SClaims§! or on enacting §SEdicts§!. \n\n£unity£ §HUnity§! is primarily gained from planetary buildings, and is used to adopt new §STraditions§!."
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_ABSTRACT_RESOURCES_DESC:0 "概念资源指代非物质性资产例如£influence£§S影响力§!和£unity£§S凝聚力§!。\n\n£influence£§S影响力§!可以通过将其他帝国变为我们的§S宿敌§!或§S保护国§!来获得。影响力一般用于建设§S恒星基地§!或设立§S宣称§!扩张你的帝国边境，或可以用来执行§S法令§!。\n\n£unity£§H凝聚力§!主要通过恒星上的建筑获取，并可以用于采纳新的§S传统§!。"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_STRATEGIC_RESOURCES_TITLE:0 "Strategic Resources"
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_STRATEGIC_RESOURCES_TITLE:0 "战略资源"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_STRATEGIC_RESOURCES_DESC:0 "Strategic Resources are rare and required to build and maintain advanced buildings and ship components. They are much harder to obtain than basic resources and are therefore also highly valued. Natural strategic resource deposits are always visible but require specific §STechnologies§! to exploit."
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_STRATEGIC_RESOURCES_DESC:0 "战略资源较为稀有，且在建造和维护高级建筑以及舰船部件时不可或缺。它们比基础资源更加难以获取，因此具有极高价值。天然的战略资源矿藏总是可见的，但需要特定的§S科技§!才能加以利用。"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_TRADE_VALUE_TITLE:0 "Trade Value"
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_TRADE_VALUE_TITLE:0 "贸易额"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_TRADE_VALUE_DESC:1 "£trade_value£ §STrade Value§! is derived from civilian day to day economic activity. \n\nIf connected to your £planet£ §SCaptial Planet§! through a §STrade Route§!, the §SStarbase§! will provide the £trade_value£ §STrade Value§! of a system in the form of £energy£ §SEnergy Credits§!, £consumer_goods£ §SConsumer Goods§! or £unity£ §SUnity§!, based on the trade policy of the §SEmpire§!."
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_TRADE_VALUE_DESC:1 "£trade_value£§S贸易额§!由市民的日常经济活动产生。\n\n如果一座§S恒星基地§!通过§S贸易路线§!连接至您的£planet£§S首都行星§!，它将会以£energy£§S能量币§!、£consumer_goods£§S消费品§!或£unity£§S凝聚力§!的形式将星系内收集到的£trade_value£§S贸易额§!提供给你，具体形式视你的§S帝国§!采纳的贸易政策决定。"
