CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_PLANET_MANAGEMENT_TITLE:0 "行星管理"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_PLANET_MANAGEMENT_DESC:0 "Planetary Management involves £district£ §SDistrict Creation§!, £building£ §SBuilding Construction§!, managing the £pops£ §SPopulation§! and its growth, as well as setting up garrisons for planetary defenses. \n\n£planet£ §SPlanets§! are a vital part of a galactic §SEmpire§! as they provide the overwhelming majority of §SResources§! and the £pops£ §SPopulation§! required for an §SEmpire§! to grow and prosper. "
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_PLANET_MANAGEMENT_DESC:0 "行星管理包括£district£§S区划建造§!、£building£§S建筑建设§!和£pops£§S人口§!的管理和增长，以及设立行星防卫部队。\n\n£planet£§S行星§!是一个星际§S帝国§!的重要组成部分，它们产出绝大部分的§S资源§!和£pops£§S人口§!，保障你的§S帝国§!繁荣发展。 "
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_PLANET_MANAGEMENT_INSTRUCTIONS:1 "§Y1.§! Select a planet (available in the Outliner on the right side of the screen).\n§Y2.§! Click on an empty Building Slot.\n§Y3.§! Build Resource Silos."
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_PLANET_MANAGEMENT_INSTRUCTIONS:1 "§Y1.§! 选择一颗行星（在屏幕右侧的总览）\n§Y2.§! 点击一处空闲的建筑槽。\n§Y3.§! 建造资源仓库。"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_PLANET_MANAGEMENT_ACTION:0 "Go to Capital Planet"
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_PLANET_MANAGEMENT_ACTION:0 "前往首都行星"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_SHIPS_TITLE:0 "Constructing Ships"
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_SHIPS_TITLE:0 "建造舰船"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_SHIPS_DESC:0 "All ships are constructed and repaired at §SStarbases§! where there is a §SShipyard Module§!. Ships are classified into civilian and military vessels. \n\nCivilian ships include £science_ship£ §SScience Ships§!, £construction_ship£ §SConstruction Ships§! and \n£colony_ship£ §SColony Ships§!. \n\n§SMilitary Ships§! represent all armed vessels of an Empire and unlike civilian ships they can be grouped together into §SFleets§! that can be led by an §SAdmiral§!"
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_SHIPS_DESC:0 "所有的舰船都是在设有§S船坞模块§!的§S恒星基地§!进行建造和维修的。舰船则分为民用和军用舰船。\n\n民用舰船包括£science_ship£§S科研船§!、£construction_ship£§S工程船§!和\n£colony_ship£§S殖民船§!。\n\n§S军用舰船§!包括帝国所有的武装舰船，与民用舰船不同，它们可以组合成§S舰队§!并由一名§S舰队司令§!指挥。"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_SHIPS_INSTRUCTIONS:1 "§Y1.§! Select the Shipyard (available in the Outliner on the right side of the screen).\n§Y2.§! Click on the Shipyard tab.\n§Y3.§! Build a Science Ship."
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_SHIPS_INSTRUCTIONS:1 "§Y1.§! 在总览（屏幕右侧）中选择您的船坞。\n§Y2.§! 在船坞窗口的下方选择船坞选项卡。\n§Y3.§! 建造一艘科研船。"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_SHIPS_ACTION:0 "Go to a Starbase with a Shipyard"
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_SHIPS_ACTION:0 "前往一座带有船坞的恒星基地"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_FIRST_CONTACT_TITLE:0 "Making First Contact"
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_FIRST_CONTACT_TITLE:0 "进行第一次接触"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_FIRST_CONTACT_DESC:1 "When encountering a new alien species for the first time, a series of challenges must be completed by an envoy. How you choose to handle these challenges will influence their opinion of your Empire."
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_FIRST_CONTCN2ACT_INSTRUCTIONS:1 "§Y1.§! 探索星系，发现另一个帝国。\n§Y2.§! 前往情报日志并点选接触事件。\n§Y3.§! 指派一名特使与其他帝国建立外交渠道。"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_FIRST_CONTACT_ACTION:0 "Open Diplomacy View"
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_FIRST_CONTACT_ACTION:0 "打开外交界面"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_PRIMITIVE_SPECIES_TITLE:0 "Encountering Primitive Species"
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_PRIMITIVE_SPECIES_TITLE:0 "遭遇土著物种"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_PRIMITIVE_SPECIES_DESC:0 "Some civilizations have yet to develop the §STechnology§! necessary for interstellar space travel. By building an §SObservation Post§! that orbits their £planet£ §SPlanet§!, you may choose to observe and study them while gaining a boost to your £society£ §SSociety Research§!. Or you may choose to uplift them with your superior technology. \n\nUplifted species become part of the Empire that uplifted them and also grants 500 £influence£ §SInfluence§!."
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_PRIMITIVE_SPECIES_DESC:0 "有些文明还未发展出足以在星际空间旅行的必要§S科技§!。通过在他们的£planet£§S行星§!轨道上建立§S观测站§!你可以选择对其进行观测或研究，以获取£society£§S社会学研究§!增益。您还可以利用您优越的科技将其提升。\n\n提升后的物种将会成为提升他们的帝国的一份子，并给予500点£influence£§S影响力§!。"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_PRIMITIVE_SPECIES_INSTRUCTIONS:1 "§Y1.§! Select the Construction Ship (available in the Outliner on the right side of the screen)\n§Y2.§! Open the Galaxy View (bottom of the screen).\n§Y3.§! Right-click on the system where a primitive species live.\n§Y4.§! Select Build Observation Post."
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_PRIMITIVE_SPECIES_INSTRUCTIONS:1 "§Y1.§! 在屏幕右侧的总览中选择工程船。\n§Y2.§! 打开星系视图（屏幕下方中央）。\n§Y3.§! 选择一个已拥有的星系，右键单击。\n§Y4.§! 点选建造观测站。"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_PRIMITIVE_SPECIES_ACTION:0 "Go to a Primitive Species"
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_PRIMITIVE_SPECIES_ACTION:0 "前往一个土著物种"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_ENVOYS_TITLE:0 "Assigning Envoys"
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_ENVOYS_TITLE:0 "指派特使"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_ENVOYS_DESC:0 "§SEnvoys§! are minor Leaders and can be assigned to various diplomatic tasks, such as improving your relationship with another £empire£ §SEmpire§! or establishing contact with newly discovered §SEmpires§!. Once an §SEnvoy§! is assigned to a task it cannot be reassigned again for a year. \n\n §SEnvoys§! are vital in managing the £opinion£ §SOpinion§! of your £empire£ §SEmpire§! among the other civilizations out there."
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_ENVOYS_DESC:0 "§S特使§!是可以被指派进行各种外交任务的低级领袖，他们可以改善您与其他£empire£§S帝国§!的关系，或与新发现的§S帝国§!建立联系。当指派一位§S特使§!进行某项任务时，一年之内无法再次调整其任务指派。\n\n§S特使§!在管理你的£empire£§S帝国§!在其他文明中的£opinion£§S评价§!方面非常重要。"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_ENVOYS_INSTRUCTIONS:0 "§Y1.§! Click on Contacts in the left navigation panel.\n§Y2.§! Select an Empire you want to improve relations with.\n§Y3.§! Click on Diplomacy.\n§Y4.§! Click on Improve Relations."
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_ENVOYS_INSTRUCTIONS:0 "§Y1.§! 在左侧导航面板点击联络\n§Y2.§! 选择一个您想提升关系的帝国。\n§Y3.§! 点击外交。\n§Y4.§! 点击提升关系。"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_ENVOYS_ACTION:0 ""
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_ENVOYS_ACTION:0 ""
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_INTEL_TITLE:0 "Gathering Intel"
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_INTEL_TITLE:0 "获取情报"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_INTEL_DESC:1 "§SIntelligence§! can be used to weaken or gain advantages over other £empire£ §SEmpires§!. The amount of information an Empire holds over another is represented by the §SIntel§! resource. \n\nThe more §SIntel§! you have on another £empire£ §SEmpire§!, the more accurate your information will be."
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_INTEL_DESC:1 "§S情报§!可以用于削弱其他£empire£§S帝国§!或获取相对优势。一个帝国掌握其他帝国的情报量由§S情报§!资源来表示。\n\n您拥有关于另一个£empire£§S帝国§!的§S情报§!越多，您对其信息掌握的就越准确。"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_INTEL_INSTRUCTIONS:0 "§Y1.§! Click on Contacts in the left navigation panel.\n§Y2.§! Select an Empire you want to learn more about.\n§Y3.§! Click on Diplomacy.\n§Y4.§! Click on Build Spy Network."
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_INTEL_INSTRUCTIONS:0 "§Y1.§! 在左侧导航面板点击联络\n§Y2.§! 选择一个你想了解更充分的帝国。\n§Y3.§! 点击外交。\n§Y4.§! 点击建立间谍网。"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_INTEL_ACTION:0 ""
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_INTEL_ACTION:0 ""
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_GALACTIC_COMMUNITY_TITLE:0 "Joining a Galactic Community"
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_GALACTIC_COMMUNITY_TITLE:0 "加入星海共同体"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_GALACTIC_COMMUNITY_DESC:1 "£empire£ §SEmpires§! that have met a majority of all other spacefaring civilizations will be invited to join the Galactic Community. Being a member allows them to vote on new laws in the senate. Laws that are passed will be enforced for all other members."
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_GALACTIC_COMMUNITY_DESC:1 "已经接触了大多数其他星际文明的 £empire£ §S帝国§!会被邀请加入星海共同体。成为成员国后就可以在参议院中对新法律投票。投票通过的法律将于全部成员国施行。"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_GALACTIC_COMMUNITY_INSTRUCTIONS:0 "So this is how liberty dies...\n...with thunderous applause."
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_GALACTIC_COMMUNITY_INSTRUCTIONS:0 "所以自由就是这般消逝……\n……伴随着雷鸣般的掌声。"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_GALACTIC_COMMUNITY_ACTION:0 ""
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_GALACTIC_COMMUNITY_ACTION:0 ""
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_FALLEN_EMPIRES_TITLE:0 "Fallen Empires"
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_FALLEN_EMPIRES_TITLE:0 "失落帝国"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_FALLEN_EMPIRES_DESC:0 "Fallen Empires are the stagnant remnants of the galactic powers of old. Though mere shadows of what they once were, they still possess incredibly advanced technology. Galactic affairs are of little interest to them, and they rarely venture beyond their own space."
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_FALLEN_EMPIRES_DESC:0 "失落帝国是残存的远古星际势力。虽然已不复往昔，但是它们仍然持有着极其先进的科技。星际事务根本无法吸引它们，而它们也几乎不踏出自己的领域。"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_TRADITIONS_TITLE:0 "Adopting Traditions"
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_TRADITIONS_TITLE:0 "采纳传统"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_TRADITIONS_DESC:0 "§STraditions§! are adopted using £unity£ §HUnity§! and allows an Empire to specialize in a given direction, such as military and rapid expansion, or diplomacy and creating federations. \n\nCompleting a §STradition Tree§! allows the £empire£ §SEmpire§! to pick an §SAscension Perk§! to further enhance itself."
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_TRADITIONS_DESC:0 "采纳§S传统§!需要花费 £unity£ §H凝聚力§!，可以让帝国专精于给定的方向，诸如军事与迅速扩张，或是外交及创建联邦。\n\n完成整支§S传统树§!后，£empire£ §S帝国§!可以挑选一项§S飞升天赋§!来进一步强化自身。"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_TRADITIONS_INSTRUCTIONS:0 "§Y1.§! Open Society Management in the left navigation panel.\n§Y2.§! Select a Tradition to adopt."
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_TRADITIONS_INSTRUCTIONS:0 "§Y1.§! 打开左侧导航面板中的社会管理。\n§Y2.§! 选择一项传统进行采纳。"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_TRADITIONS_ACTION:0 "Open Traditions View"
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_TRADITIONS_ACTION:0 "打开传统界面"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_POLICIES_TITLE:0 "Settling Policies"
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_POLICIES_TITLE:0 "设定政策"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_POLICIES_DESC:0 "§SPolicies§! define our £empire£ §SEmpire's§! attitude towards various matters: how aggressive our Empire is, how we treat our £pops£ citizens, what we view as acceptable and what isn't. \n\n§SPolicies§! are different from §SEdicts§! in that they cost nothing to implement, but have effects on how other Empires are likely to view us."
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_POLICIES_DESC:0 "§S政策§!规定了我们的 £empire£ §S帝国§!在处理诸般事务时的态度：我国有多么激进好战，我国如何对待本国 £pops£ 公民，以及哪些是我们可以接受的，而哪些不能。\n\n§S政策§!不同于§S法令§!，其无需花费代价就能实施，但会对其他帝国可能如何看待我们产生影响。"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_POLICIES_INSTRUCTIONS:1 "§Y1.§! Open Policies in the left navigation panel.\n§Y2.§! Click on Diplomatic stance.\n§Y3.§! Choose one that suits you."
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_POLICIES_INSTRUCTIONS:1 "§Y1.§! 在左侧导航面板打开政策视图。\n§Y2.§! 点击外交姿态。\n§Y3.§! 选择合适的外交姿态。"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_POLICIES_ACTION:0 "Open Policies View"
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_POLICIES_ACTION:0 "打开政策视图"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_LEADERS_TITLE:0 "Employing Leaders"
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_LEADERS_TITLE:0 "雇佣领袖"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_LEADERS_DESC:1 "§SLeaders§! are your §SScientists§!, §SAdmirals§!, §SGenerals§! and §SGovernors§!. \n\nYou are advised to have leaders for your §SMilitary Fleets§!, for governing your newly colonized £planet£ §SPlanet§! and for leading your £science_ship£ §SScience Ships§! that are sent on exploration missions."
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_LEADERS_DESC:1 "§S领袖§!就是你的§S科学家§!、§S舰队司令§!、§S陆军将领§!和§S总督§!。\n\n你最好指派领袖以率领§S军用舰队§!，管辖新殖民的£planet£§S行星§!以及指挥£science_ship£§S科研船§!进行探索任务。"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_LEADERS_INSTRUCTIONS:0 "§Y1.§! Open Leaders in the left navigation panel.\n§Y2.§! Recruit a Scientist that you can assign to a new science ship later."
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_LEADERS_INSTRUCTIONS:0 "§Y1.§! 在左侧导航面板打开领袖。\n§Y2.§! 招募一名科学家，以便之后指派其指挥新的科研船。"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_LEADERS_ACTION:0 "Open Leaders View"
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_LEADERS_ACTION:0 "打开领袖界面"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_EDICTS_TITLE:0 "Enacting Edicts"
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_EDICTS_TITLE:0 "施行法令"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_EDICTS_DESC:0 "Edicts are Empire modifiers with a fixed cost that an Empire may choose to apply. New edicts must be unlocked through research or events. Continuous edicts can be activated or deactivated anytime by spending Influence."
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_EDICTS_DESC:0 "法令是一个帝国可以选择性实施的具有特定花费的帝国修正。新的法令必须通过研究或事件来解锁。持续性法令可以在任何时候花费影响力来激活或停用。"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_SPECIES_MANAGEMENT_TITLE:0 "Keeping a Population Happy"
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_SPECIES_MANAGEMENT_TITLE:0 "保持人口幸福度"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_SPECIES_MANAGEMENT_DESC:0 "A happy £pops£ §SPopulation§! is a productive £pops£ §SPopulation§!. \nBut maintaining §SHappiness§! can be tricky, and if unhappiness is left unchecked, it can foster §SUnrest§!. \n\nFortunately, there are many ways to improve happiness on a £planet£ §SPlanet§!. Planetary §SPolicies§! and §SEdicts§!, §SCivics§!, §SSpecies Rights§!, §SBuildings§!, and §SRuler Traits§! can all positively affect §SHappiness§!."
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_SPECIES_MANAGEMENT_DESC:0 "开心的£pops£§S人口§!也是高产的£pops£§S人口§!。\n但维持§S幸福度§!并不容易，如果让低幸福度持续，甚至可能造成§S不满§!。\n\n幸好我们有许多方法来提升£planet£§S行星§!上的幸福度。行星§S政策§!和§S法令§!、§S国民理念§!、§S物种权利§!、§S建筑§!以及§S统治者特质§!均可以对§S幸福度§!产生正面影响。"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_SPECIES_MANAGEMENT_INSTRUCTIONS:0 "§Y1.§! Select a planet (available in the Outliner on the right side of the screen).\n§Y2.§! Click on an empty Building Slot.\n§Y3.§! Build Holo-Theatres."
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_SPECIES_MANAGEMENT_INSTRUCTIONS:0 "§Y1.§! 选择一颗行星（在屏幕右侧的总览）\n§Y2.§! 点击一处空闲的建筑槽。\n§Y3.§! 建造全息影像剧场。"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_SPECIES_MANAGEMENT_ACTION:0 "Open Species View"
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_SPECIES_MANAGEMENT_ACTION:0 "打开物种界面"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_FACTIONS_TITLE:0 "Managing Factions"
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_FACTIONS_TITLE:0 "管理派系"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_FACTIONS_DESC:0 " §HFactions§! represent political parties and are supported by §HPops§! with matching ethics. Fulfilling issues by a Faction will raise their Approval and the associated happiness of all Pops that has joined it. A happy faction will also generate £unity£ §HUnity§!."
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_FACTIONS_DESC:0 " §H派系§!表示由相应思潮的§H人口§!所支持的政治团体。满足相应派系所提出的诉求可以提升他们的支持度和加入其中的所有人口的幸福度。幸福度高的派系将产出£unity£§H凝聚力§!。"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_CASUS_BELLI_TITLE:0 "Declaring War"
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_CASUS_BELLI_TITLE:0 "宣战"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_CASUS_BELLI_DESC:0 "In order for an £empire£ §SEmpire§! to start a §SWar§!, it needs a Casus Belli - a reason to declare §SWar§!. A Casus Belli may range from merely humiliating a §SRival§! to exterminating another species. \n\n§SWars§! can end in two ways: With the §SSurrender§! of either side or with a negotiated §SStatus Quo§! peace."
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_CASUS_BELLI_DESC:0 "£empire£§S帝国§!要开始一场§S战争§!需要战争理由，即向他国§S宣战§!的具体缘由。战争理由多种多样，可以是羞辱§S宿敌§!甚至是灭绝其他种族。\n\n§S战争§!有两种途径结束：其中一方§S投降§!，或经过协商达成§S维持现状§!和平。"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_CASUS_BELLI_INSTRUCTIONS:0 "Choose your enemy wisely. \n§Y1.§! Open Contacts in the left navigation panel.\n§Y2.§! Select an Empire you want to attack.\n§Y3.§! Open Diplomacy.\n§Y4.§! Click on Declare War."
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_CASUS_BELLI_INSTRUCTIONS:0 "谨慎地选择您的敌人。\n§Y1.§! 在左侧导航面板点击联络。\n§Y2.§! 选择一个您想进攻的帝国。\n§Y3.§! 点击外交。\n§Y4.§! 点击宣战。"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_CASUS_BELLI_ACTION:0 "Open Diplomacy View"
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_CASUS_BELLI_ACTION:0 "打开外交界面"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_CLAIMS_TITLE:0 "Getting Claims"
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_CLAIMS_TITLE:0 "设置宣称"
CHANGE HELP_TUTORIAL_CLAIMS_TITLE:0 "设置领土主张"
ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_CLAIMS_DESC:0 "§SClaims§! cost £influence£ §SInfluence§! and represent territorial ambitions. \n\nDuring a §SWar§!, §SClaims§! may be pressed to determine what §SSystems§! the victor will gain. It is possible to claim the same §SSystem§! multiple times to gain a stronger §SClaim§! on it, which can outbid the competing claims of §SAllies§! when going to §SWar§! together."
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_CLAIMS_DESC:0 "§S宣称§!会花费 £influence£ §S影响力§!，代表领土野心。\n\n在§S战争§!中，可以通过声索§S宣称§!，决定胜利者获得哪些§S恒星系§!。一国可以多次宣称相同的§S恒星系§!，获得更强的§S宣称§!程度，从而压过一同参与§S战争§!的§S盟友§!的宣称。"
CHANGE HELP_TUTORIAL_CLAIMS_DESC:0 "§S领土主张§!会花费 £influence£ §S影响力§!，代表领土野心。\n\n在§S战争§!中，可以通过声索§S领土主张§!，决定胜利者获得哪些§S星系§!。一国可以多次宣称相同的§S星系§!所有权，获得更强的§S领土主张§!程度，从而压过一同参与§S战争§!的§S盟友§!的宣称。"
