ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_SHIP_DESIGN_DESC:1 "By default, Ship Designs will be auto generated and updated, but to get the edge over tougher opponents you may want to create ship designs that counter the hostile fleet. Shields are tough against lasers, but vulnerable to missiles, while a strong hull protects against ballistics better than against energy weapons."
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_SHIP_DESIGN_DESC:1 "默认情况下，舰船设计会自动生成、升级，但若想要对强大的敌人获得优势，你可能想要针对敌军的舰船作克制性的设计。护盾可以有效抵挡激光，但对导弹时形同虚设，而坚固的船体护甲面对炮火时则可以提供更好的防护，但对能量武器较为虚弱。"
