ADD HELP_TUTORIAL_CRISIS_DESC:0 "A §SCrisis§! threatens the entire §SGalaxy§! and all life within it. \n\nRarely will you be ready to face a §SCrisis§! on your own. Each time a crisis conquers a £planet£ §SPlanet§! it causes diplomatic §SThreat§! with all £empire£ §SEmpires§!, making them more likely to cooperate against the §SCrisis§!. \n\nEndgame Crises have a §SSituation Log§! (£f2£) entry that keeps count of the casualties on both sides and shows how close the §SCrisis§! is to being defeated."
CN2 HELP_TUTORIAL_CRISIS_DESC:0 "§S危机§!威胁到整个§S星系§!和其中的一切生命。\n\n您通常不会独自面对§S危机§!。每当危机征服一颗£planet£§S行星§!，它就会对全体£empire£§S帝国§!产生外交§S威胁§!，使得他们更有可能合作起来对抗§S危机§!。\n\n终末危机拥有§S情报日志§!（£f2£）条目，可以使您持续获悉双方的伤亡，以及显示距离§S危机§!被击败还有多远。"
